    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present an exemplary specimen of automotive preservation. This vehicle is offered in pristine condition, having been maintained to a standard that mirrors its original factory delivery. The exterior retains a flawless finish, complemented by an interior that exhibits no signs of wear. Mechanically beyond reproach and aesthetically superior, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
