    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she\u2019s a total gem! This car is in truly spectacular condition\u2014honestly, it\u2019s like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this ride from day one, keeping it spotless and garage-stored. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and cared for perfectly, this is the one for you. Swing by and see it for yourself!",
      "price": 46500.0,
