    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-revving masterpiece utilizes individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock, the drivetrain remains in peak mechanical synchrony. The chassis is structurally immaculate; the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearings have been replaced with treated shells to ensure longevity. Suspension geometry remains true with crisp turn-in facilitated by fresh bushings and original dampers. The exterior retains its factory-applied finish with consistent micron readings across all panels, while the interior features Nappa leather with zero bolster wear. This is a turn-key example for the discerning driver seeking the pinnacle of analog feedback and mechanical purity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
